ified":1679287191,"replies":17,"id":925510},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1670739760","name":"career","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1670739760","title":"职场话题","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","topics":14106,"footer":"","header":"这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。","title_alternative":"Career","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1670739760","stars":2635,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":770,"parent_node_name":"work"},"member":{"id":460950,"username":"YadongZhang","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/YadongZhang","website":"zhyd1997.eth.limo","twitter":"zhyd007","psn":"","github":"zhyd1997","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f71e/defc/460950_mini.png?m=1677726872","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f71e/defc/460950_normal.png?m=1677726872","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f71e/defc/460950_large.png?m=1677726872","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f71e/defc/460950_xlarge.png?m=1677726872","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f71e/defc/460950_xlarge.png?m=1677726872","created":1577155776,"last_modified":1677726872},"last_reply_by":"chengsitom","last_touched":1679294651,"title":"[分享] 作为一名前端工程师，我是怎么拿到新加坡 full-time 职位 offer 的","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/925511","created":1679287597,"deleted":0,"content":"看到很多人都在焦虑找不到工作，分享一下可以尝试的其他方式，或许有点帮助\r\n\r\n------\r\n去年 11 月份检索 Nextjs 官方 github 上的 issue 的时候，偶然看到有求职板块和招聘讨论区\r\n\r\n这两个板块每个月的月初会创建新的帖子，而且很多岗位都是远程的，目前是 3 月份的：\r\n\r\n**[谁在找工作]( https://github.com/vercel/next.js/discussions/46890)**\r\n\r\n**[谁在招人]( https://github.com/vercel/next.js/discussions/46889)**\r\n\r\n-----\r\n\r\n当时 Freelance 机会是在上面找到的，时薪也很高，那边公司直接从 Github 上的邮箱联系到我，然后现在拿到了新加坡一家小小公司的全职 offer ，当然也有运气的成分\r\n\r\n![offer screenshot]( https://ik.imagekit.io/1winv85cn8g/sg-offer-screenshot_lbjyYiyKK.png?updatedAt=1679285898012)\r\n\r\n（鄙人技术方面不大自信，Freelance 的时候完全没压力，现在全职了就有点担心过不了试用期😓😂。。。\r\n\r\n有求职（ full-time / contractor ）或者招聘需求的可以在上面试试看\r\n\r\n------\r\n写了一大堆不知道是不是 v 友想了解的，其他想问的可以留言","content_rendered":"<p>看到很多人都在焦虑找不到工作，分享一下可以尝试的其他方式，或许有点帮助</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>去年 11 月份检索 Nextjs 官方 github 上的 issue 的时候，偶然看到有求职板块和招聘讨论区</p>\n<p>这两个板块每个月的月初会创建新的帖子，而且很多岗位都是远程的，目前是 3 月份的：</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/vercel/next.js/discussions/46890\" rel=\"nofollow\">谁在找工作</a></strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/vercel/next.js/discussions/46889\" rel=\"nofollow\">谁在招人</a></strong></p>\n<hr/>\n<p>当时 Freelance 机会是在上面找到的，时薪也很高，那边公司直接从 Github 上的邮箱联系到我，然后现在拿到了新加坡一家小小公司的全职 offer ，当然也有运气的成分</p>\n<p><img alt=\"offer screenshot\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/1winv85cn8g/sg-offer-screenshot_lbjyYiyKK.png?updatedAt=1679285898012\"/></p>\n<p>（鄙人技术方面不大自信，Freelance 的时候完全没压力，现在全职了就有点担心过不了试用期😓😂。。。</p>\n<p>有求职（ full-time / contractor ）或者招聘需求的可以在上面试试看</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>写了一大堆不知道是不是 v 友想了解的，其他想问的可以留言</p>\n","last_modified":1679287742,"replies":16,"id":925511},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_large.png?m=1650127281","name":"share","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_normal.png?m=1650127281","title":"分享发现","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","topics":37845,"footer":"","header":"分享你看到的好玩的，有信息量的，欢迎从这里获取灵感。","title_alternative":"Share","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1650127281","stars":5265,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":16,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":123399,"username":"yuhuan66666","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/yuhuan66666","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6840671dff0dd2c7676f1d1e4b2cb046?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6840671dff0dd2c7676f1d1e4b2cb046?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/684067